lead_paragraph: Five-times PGA Tour winner Jimmy Walker led by one stroke when rain and extremely strong winds forced the suspension of play for the day during the final round at the Farmers Insurance Open on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Walker Leads as Final Round Goes Into Monday at Torrey Pines
